</style></head><body><div class="container">
<h1>Kafka Security Audit Report</h1>
<div class="grade grade-d">Grade: D</div><div class="summary"><div class="card"><h3>Total</h3><div class="num">45</div></div><div class="card"><h3>Passed</h3><div class="num pass">29</div></div><div class="card"><h3>Warnings</h3><div class="num warn">15</div></div><div class="card"><h3>Failures</h3><div class="num fail">1</div></div></div><table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>CIS</th><th>Check</th><th>Severity</th><th>Detail</th><th>Remediation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="status-fail">✗</td><td>CIS-4.1</td><td>SASL Authentication</td><td>HIGH</td><td>No SASL mechanisms configured — any client can connect</td><td>Set listener.security.protocol.map and sasl.enabled.mechanisms in broker config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-4.2</td><td>No Plaintext Listeners</td><td>HIGH</td><td>All listeners use TLS or SASL</td><td>Change listener protocol to SASL_SSL in kafka.listeners configuration</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-5.1</td><td>ACL Authorization</td><td>HIGH</td><td>Authorizer: org.apache.kafka.metadata.authorizer.StandardAuthorizer</td><td>Set kafka.authorization.type: simple in values.yaml</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-5.2</td><td>ACL Rules Defined</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>31 ACL rules active</td><td>Define KafkaUser resources with acls in values.yaml users section</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-5.3</td><td>No Wildcard Topic ACLs</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>8 wildcard ALLOW rules — overly permissive</td><td>Replace wildcard ACLs with topic-specific ALLOW rules</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.1</td><td>Unclean Election Disabled</td><td>CRITICAL</td><td>Unclean leader election disabled — data integrity protected</td><td>Set unclean.leader.election.enable: false in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.2</td><td>Auto-Create Topics Disabled</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Topic auto-creation disabled</td><td>Set auto.create.topics.enable: false in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.3</td><td>Message Size Bounded</td><td>LOW</td><td>message.max.bytes = 10.0MB</td><td>Set message.max.bytes to ≤20MB in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.4</td><td>Min ISR ≥ 2</td><td>HIGH</td><td>min.insync.replicas = 2</td><td>Set min.insync.replicas: 2 in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.5</td><td>Replication Factor ≥ 3</td><td>HIGH</td><td>default.replication.factor = 3</td><td>Set default.replication.factor: 3 in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.3</td><td>Inter-Broker Encryption</td><td>HIGH</td><td>Inter-broker traffic is unencrypted: PLAINTEXT</td><td>Set security.inter.broker.protocol: SASL_SSL in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.6</td><td>Default Cleanup Policy</td><td>LOW</td><td>log.cleanup.policy = delete</td><td>Use log.cleanup.policy=compact for changelog topics</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-6.1</td><td>Connection Rate Limiting</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Connection limits configured</td><td>Set max.connections and max.connection.creation.rate per listener</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-6.2</td><td>Default Quotas Set</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>No default quotas — one client can monopolize cluster bandwidth</td><td>Set quotas in KafkaUser spec: producerByteRate and consumerByteRate</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-4.4</td><td>TLS Protocol Version</td><td>HIGH</td><td>ssl.protocol = TLSv1.3</td><td>Set ssl.protocol: TLSv1.3 in kafka.config</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-5.6</td><td>Super Users Audited</td><td>HIGH</td><td>No super users configured</td><td>Minimize super.users — use ACLs for fine-grained access instead</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.10</td><td>SASL Mechanism Strength</td><td>HIGH</td><td>No SASL mechanisms configured</td><td>Use SCRAM-SHA-512 instead of PLAIN for password-based auth</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-5.7</td><td>DENY Rules Defined</td><td>LOW</td><td>No DENY rules — relying solely on ALLOW whitelist</td><td>Add DENY rules for sensitive topics/operations as defense in depth</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.11</td><td>SSL Keystore Configured</td><td>HIGH</td><td>No SSL keystore — TLS not available</td><td>Configure ssl.keystore.location with broker certificate</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.12</td><td>SSL Truststore Configured</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>No SSL truststore — cannot verify client certs</td><td>Configure ssl.truststore.location for client certificate validation</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.13</td><td>mTLS Enforcement</td><td>HIGH</td><td>ssl.client.auth = none — clients not required to present certificates</td><td>Set ssl.client.auth: required for mTLS</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.7</td><td>Log Retention Configured</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Retention: 24h</td><td>Set log.retention.hours between 24 and 720 (1-30 days)</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.8</td><td>Controlled Shutdown</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>controlled.shutdown.enable = true</td><td>Set controlled.shutdown.enable: true</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-3.9</td><td>Delete Topic Enabled</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>delete.topic.enable = true — authorized users can permanently delete topics</td><td>Consider delete.topic.enable: false and use ACLs to control deletion</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.10</td><td>Transaction Log Replication</td><td>HIGH</td><td>transaction.state.log.replication.factor = 3</td><td>Set transaction.state.log.replication.factor: 3</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-6.3</td><td>Request Size Limits</td><td>LOW</td><td>socket.request.max.bytes = 100.0MB</td><td>Set socket.request.max.bytes to limit individual request size</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.11</td><td>Background Threads</td><td>LOW</td><td>background.threads = 10</td><td>Set background.threads >= 10 for production workloads</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.12</td><td>Offset Retention</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>offsets.retention.minutes = 10080 (7 days)</td><td>Set offsets.retention.minutes >= 10080 (7 days)</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.13</td><td>Log Segment Size</td><td>LOW</td><td>log.segment.bytes = 1.0GB</td><td>Set log.segment.bytes between 100MB and 1GB</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.14</td><td>Compression Policy</td><td>LOW</td><td>compression.type = producer</td><td>Set compression.type to lz4 or zstd for bandwidth savings</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-4.5</td><td>SSL Cipher Suites</td><td>HIGH</td><td>Using JVM default ciphers (secure)</td><td>Remove RC4, DES, MD5, NULL ciphers from ssl.cipher.suites</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.6</td><td>SSL Hostname Verification</td><td>HIGH</td><td>ssl.endpoint.identification.algorithm = HTTPS — hostname verification DISABLED, vulnerable to MITM</td><td>Set ssl.endpoint.identification.algorithm: https</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-4.7</td><td>SSL Enabled Protocols</td><td>HIGH</td><td>Protocols: TLSv1.2,TLSv1.3</td><td>Remove SSLv3 and TLSv1.0 from ssl.enabled.protocols</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-3.15</td><td>Topics with RF=1</td><td>HIGH</td><td>1 topics have RF=1 — single point of failure</td><td>Increase replication.factor to at least 2 for all production topics</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.16</td><td>Under-Replicated Partitions</td><td>CRITICAL</td><td>All partitions fully replicated</td><td>Investigate broker health — under-replicated partitions indicate failing nodes</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-3.17</td><td>Internal Topic Protection</td><td>HIGH</td><td>__consumer_offsets not found</td><td>Set offsets.topic.replication.factor: 3</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.18</td><td>Topic Count</td><td>LOW</td><td>12 user topics</td><td>Consider consolidating topics or partitioning strategy if count exceeds 1000</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-6.4</td><td>Max Connections Per IP</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>No per-IP connection limit — single host can exhaust all connections</td><td>Set max.connections.per.ip to limit connection exhaustion from single host</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-6.5</td><td>Network Threads</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>num.network.threads = 5</td><td>Set num.network.threads >= 3 (typically 8 for production)</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-6.6</td><td>IO Threads</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>num.io.threads = 8</td><td>Set num.io.threads >= 8 for production workloads</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-4.8</td><td>Listener Protocol Map</td><td>HIGH</td><td>Protocol map: CONTROLPLANE-9090:SSL,REPLICATION-9091:SSL,PLAIN-9092:SASL_PLAINTEXT,TLS-9093:SSL,EXTERNAL-9094:SASL_SSL</td><td>Map all listeners to SASL_SSL or SSL in listener.security.protocol.map</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-3.19</td><td>Log Flush Interval</td><td>MEDIUM</td><td>Using OS-level fsync only — may lose data on power failure</td><td>Set log.flush.interval.ms or log.flush.interval.messages for durability vs performance trade-off</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.20</td><td>Group Coordinator Replication</td><td>HIGH</td><td>offsets.topic.replication.factor = 3</td><td>Set offsets.topic.replication.factor: 3</td></tr><tr><td class="status-pass">✓</td><td>CIS-3.21</td><td>Leader Imbalance Threshold</td><td>LOW</td><td>leader.imbalance.per.broker.percentage = 10%</td><td>Keep leader.imbalance.per.broker.percentage <= 10</td></tr><tr><td class="status-warn">⚠</td><td>CIS-4.9</td><td>Delegation Token Config</td><td>LOW</td><td>No delegation token master key — tokens unavailable for short-lived clients</td><td>Configure delegation.token.master.key for short-lived client credentials</td></tr></tbody></table>
